16:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda bank omonatlar bo'yicha stavkalar milliy valyutada (so'm) yillik 20% dan 26% gacha va xorijiy valyutada (dollar/yevro) yillik 4% dan 7% gacha. So'mdagi yuqori stavkalar MB kalit stavkasi 14% va inflyatsiyani qoplash zarurati bilan bog'liq. Depozit kalkulyatori foizlar kapitalizatsiyasi, muddat va joylashtirish shartlarini hisobga olgan holda omonat bo'yicha daromadni hisoblaydi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Omonat turlari: muddatli (qat'iy stavka, muddatidan oldin yechib olishsiz), jamg'arma (to'ldirish imkoniyati bilan), talab qilib olinguncha (past stavka, erkin foydalanish). Oddiy foizlar hisobi: Daromad = Summa × Stavka × Muddat(kun) / 365. Oylik kapitalizatsiya bilan: Jami = Summa × (1 + Stavka/12)^Oylar."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash misoli: 100 000 000 so'mlik omonat 12 oyga yillik 24% da. Kapitalizatsiyasiz: daromad = 24 000 000 so'm, jami 124 000 000 so'm. Oylik kapitalizatsiya bilan: jami = 126 824 179 so'm, daromad = 26 824 179 so'm — 2 824 179 so'mga ko'proq. Kapitalizatsiyada samarali stavka: nominal 24% o'rniga 26,82%."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Depozit foizlari rezidentlar uchun 5% (norezidentlar uchun 10%) stavkada "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":"ga tortiladi. Bank foizlarni to'lashda soliqni avtomatik ravishda ushlab qoladi. Jismoniy shaxslar omonatlari Banklardagi fuqarolar omonatlarini kafolatlash fondi tomonidan bir omonatchiga bir bankda 200 000 000 so'mgacha (ekvivalent) miqdorda kafolatlanadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Daromadni maksimallashtirish uchun tavsiya etiladi: oylik kapitalizatsiyali omonatlarni tanlash; bir nechta banklarning stavkalarini solishtirish; yirik summalarni banklar o'rtasida kafolat chegarasida (bank boshiga 200 mln so'm) taqsimlash; inflyatsiyani hisobga olgan holda real daromadlilikni baholash. 7,3% inflyatsiya va 24% stavkada real daromadlilik taxminan 16,7%."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":[["$","caption",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 text-left font-medium text-foreground bg-muted/50 border-b border-border","children":"O'zbekiston banklarida omonat stavkalari (12 oy)"}],"$L1c","$L1d"]}]}]]]}],"$L1e","$L1f"]}]
